style="padding: 1em;">&#8220;Tue, 12 Feb 2013 06:58:22 +0000&#8243;</td><td
style="padding: 1em;">&#8220;adrianburch&#8221;</td></tr><tr><td
style="padding: 1em;">5</td><td
style="padding: 1em;">&#8220;http://t.co/D3KOJIvF article about Madden 2013 using AI to prodict the super bowl #databases #bus311&#8243;</td><td
